This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for understanding phrases and sentences. Specifically, it proposes using dictionary definitions to train neural language embedding models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
